---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { site } from "@data/site";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Dr Daguang Han's Founding Leadership"
  description="Evidence-focused summary of Dr Daguang Han's leadership role in SCSDA's early platform-construction period."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell split reverse">
      <figure class="image-panel">
        <img
          src="/images/lab-engagement.jpg"
          alt="Public visual record of research engagement and laboratory visit"
        />
        <figcaption class="image-caption">
          Public visual material reused from the preserved SCSDA website.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <div class="article">
        <p class="eyebrow">Application relevance</p>
        <h2>From researcher to research-platform builder.</h2>
        <p>
          For UK and European academic applications, SCSDA is most valuable as
          evidence that Dr Daguang Han has worked beyond individual publication
          output. It shows platform building, research-centre development,
          interdisciplinary coordination, applied project formation and
          international research engagement.
        </p>
        <p>
          The implementation report lists Dr Han as the responsible person for
          the SCSDA platform-construction project. Public wording on this site
          therefore uses the cautious phrase "principal responsible person and
          founding executive lead".
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section surface">
    <div class="shell section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Leadership scope</p>
        <h2>What this site can credibly evidence.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        Stronger titles such as Founding President or Chair of the Board should
        be added only when appointment, board or registration evidence is placed
        in the evidence folder and mapped in the claim register.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="shell theme-grid">
      <article class="theme-card">
        <h3>Platform planning and delivery</h3>
        <p>
          Coordinating the early-stage development of a nonprofit applied
          research platform in smart cities and sustainable infrastructure.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="theme-card">
        <h3>Research-centre development</h3>
        <p>
          Connecting BIM, digital twins, sensing, smart infrastructure and
          sustainable construction into a coherent applied research structure.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="theme-card">
        <h3>International expert engagement</h3>
        <p>
          Building links between European academic expertise, Chinese
          engineering application contexts and public-facing research outputs.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="theme-card">
        <h3>Enterprise-facing research</h3>
        <p>
          Translating digital built-environment research into non-confidential
          applied projects, training, implementation guides and validation work.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell article narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Suggested public wording</p>
      <h2>Use precise language that helps rather than distracts.</h2>
      <div class="callout">
        During SCSDA's early platform-construction period, Dr Daguang Han
        served as the principal responsible person and founding executive lead,
        coordinating research-centre development, international expert
        engagement, enterprise-facing applied research, and public
        research-platform delivery in smart cities and sustainable
        infrastructure.
      </div>
      <div class="profile-links">
        {site.profiles.map((profile) => (
          <a href={profile.href} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{profile.label}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
